---
description: Hypothesis subsystem
globs: ["src/biolit/hypothesis/**"]
alwaysApply: false
---
- LangGraph state machine: generation -> reflection -> ranking(Elo tournament) -> evolution -> (rank) ... -> meta-review.
- Generation may only assert claims it can cite; ground every seed with a retrieval call.
- Ranking is pairwise with an LLM judge; update Elo. Dedup near-duplicates before ranking.
- Meta-review outputs proposals with mechanism, experiment, explicit falsification criterion, evidence trail.
- Mandatory provenance: persist evidence rows (pmid, snippet, stance) for every hypothesis.
